# Research outputs — exclude generated run artifacts but keep committed experiment results
# The primary results (pilot CSVs + summary_metrics.json) are committed directly.
# Credibility suite and real-LLM artifacts are tracked via force-add and must be
# recommitted after any run that changes the numbers.
results/
!results/credibility/
!results/real_lm/
artifacts/

